{"tid":1825632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★噴射飛航裁員過百人 員工斥公司不近人情","createTime":"2020-01-15T12:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T19:40:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"f952a2977b5e48ac7c62eb5db1d3429bce4a534f","tid":1825632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=21a0d73f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】噴射飛航除了減薪外，原來亦裁員過百人。本月8日先裁澳門員工，翌日裁本港員工，剩下來的員工要減薪。有被裁員工向東網控訴：「公司連續咁多年都賺錢，係舊年生意跌，咁就炒人，不近人情！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該員工表示，公司原本有2000人，去年中裁了幾百人，近日再裁過百人。今次裁員涉及各部門，他年資不高，僅獲賠兩個月人工，約4萬港元。他承認近期生意差，試過一架船只得30人坐，但指公司是大企業，起碼過完年才向員工開刀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%99%B4%E5%B0%84%E9%A3%9B%E8%88%AA%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA-%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%96%A5%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%8D%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%85-090739243.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2599%25B4%25E5%25B0%2584%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2596%25A5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2583%2585-090739243.html&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=052c8b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%99%B4%E5%B0%84%E9%A3%9B%E8%88%AA%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA-%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%96%A5%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%8D%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%85-090739243.html</a>"},{"pid":"b3150190d347309c4dfbd2a996957e4be18ee624","tid":1825632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6e2e17afc30db16f5a083ea4e043919eb724e2","tid":1825632,"uid":